<span class="mvpt-section-label">How it works</span>
<h2 class="mvpt-steps__title">From first enquiry to ongoing training — three clear steps.</h2>
<div class="mvpt-steps__grid">
  <article class="mvpt-step">
    <div class="mvpt-step__num">1</div>
    <div class="mvpt-step__body">
      <h3>Book your initial consultation</h3>
      <p>Pick a 90-minute slot below or drop me a message. We'll cover your history, movement limitations, pain patterns and what you want to get back to — in detail, no pressure.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
  <article class="mvpt-step">
    <div class="mvpt-step__num">2</div>
    <div class="mvpt-step__body">
      <h3>Full biomechanical screen</h3>
      <p>A Functional Patterns postural and gait assessment to identify the compensations actually driving your pain — not just where you feel it. You leave with clarity on what's happening and why.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
  <article class="mvpt-step">
    <div class="mvpt-step__num">3</div>
    <div class="mvpt-step__body">
      <h3>Ongoing 1-on-1 training</h3>
      <p>Detailed hands-on movement instruction, tailored corrective work, and weekly homework. Clients typically train one to three times per week — the more consistent you are, the faster the change.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</div>
